720
00:56:33,400 --> 00:56:36,400
 zaustavila tu kolonu

721
00:56:36,400 --> 00:56:37,940
 i poslije toga

722
00:56:37,940 --> 00:56:39,800
 više nije bilo napada

723
00:56:39,800 --> 00:56:40,960
