726
00:56:43,480 --> 00:56:44,340
 Nebude koliko,

727
00:56:44,340 --> 00:56:46,380
 da mi ste mlađa generacija.

728
00:56:46,380 --> 00:56:49,200
 Moram ću pretimiti,

729
00:56:49,200 --> 00:56:50,180
 jer ovdje mojom izaći,

730
00:56:50,180 --> 00:56:51,840
 zbrani za poju minutu,

731
00:56:51,840 --> 00:56:53,840
 pa je da mislim što vrijeme za...

732
00:56:53,840 --> 00:56:54,440
 Ovo što je gospodin

733
00:56:54,440 --> 00:56:55,540
 zelo posvjedočio,

734
00:56:55,540 --> 00:56:57,560
 to nam je profesor Ivančić.

735
00:56:57,560 --> 00:56:59,300
 Svi znamo ko je bio

736
00:56:59,300 --> 00:57:00,680
 isto svjedočimo.

737
00:57:00,680 --> 00:57:02,180
 Ovo što je gospodin rekao,

738
00:57:02,180 --> 00:57:03,620
